org.transitime.gtfs

Class GtfsData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.transitime.gtfs.GtfsData

  • public class GtfsData
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains all the GTFS data processed into Java lists and such. Also combines in info from supplemental routes.txt file if there is one.
    Author:
    SkiBu Smith

      • getPath

        public Path getPath(java.lang.String tripPatternId,
           java.lang.String pathId)
        Returns the Path for the specified tripPatternId and pathId. Can't just use pathId since lots of trip patterns will traverse the same stops, resulting in identical pathIds. And don't want to make the pathIds themselves unique because then wouldn't be able to reuse travel time data as much.
        Parameters:
        tripPatternId -
        pathId -
